573161_normal.png?m=1703588992", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9338/a785/573161_large.png?m=1703588992", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9338/a785/573161_xlarge.png?m=1703588992", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9338/a785/573161_xlarge.png?m=1703588992", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9338/a785/573161_xlarge.png?m=1703588992", "created": 1645169499, "last_modified": 1703588992}, "last_reply_by": "FightPig", "last_touched": 1722575015, "title": "上个月电费 443 震惊到我了，你们一个月都多少电费啊（前提：民水民电）", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1061951", "created": 1722568125, "deleted": 0, "content": "平时两个人，工作日都朝九晚六。家里用电的就空调、冰箱、洗衣机、电饭煲，还有就是照明了。\r\n为啥一个月可以干到 600 多度电，根本想不通。。。\r\n坐标深圳", "content_rendered": "<p>平时两个人，工作日都朝九晚六。家里用电的就空调、冰箱、洗衣机、电饭煲，还有就是照明了。\n为啥一个月可以干到 600 多度电，根本想不通。。。\n坐标深圳</p>\n", "last_modified": 1722568172, "replies": 66, "id": 1061951}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 6148, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1489, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 693520, "username": "kong0bbs", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kong0bbs", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/457c/719b/693520_mini.png?m=1720696089", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/457c/719b/693520_normal.png?m=1720696089", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/457c/719b/693520_large.png?m=1720696089", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/457c/719b/693520_xlarge.png?m=1720696089", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/457c/719b/693520_xlarge.png?m=1720696089", "created": 1717069756, "last_modified": 1720696089}, "last_reply_by": "ziseyinzi", "last_touched": 1722574994, "title": "老婆区别对待我妹妹的女儿和我女儿，应该如何处理？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1061982", "created": 1722571670, "deleted": 0, "content": "我妹妹家女儿放暑假后来我家玩，跟我女儿玩得很开心。\r\n\r\n但我老婆带她逛了次街，她回来后就一直躲在被子里哭。\r\n\r\n问她才知道，是因为我老婆区别对待让她感到很委屈。\r\n\r\n我老婆给我女儿吃哈根达斯，却给她吃普通雪糕。\r\n\r\n我老婆给我女儿吃牛排，却给她吃烤肠。\r\n\r\n这个小女孩 5 岁了，她父母离婚多年，一直是老人在带，内心非常敏感。\r\n\r\n她感觉我老婆不喜欢自己，感觉很委屈，就躲在躲被里哭。\r\n\r\n应该如何处理？", "content_rendered": "<p>我妹妹家女儿放暑假后来我家玩，跟我女儿玩得很开心。</p>\n<p>但我老婆带她逛了次街，她回来后就一直躲在被子里哭。</p>\n<p>问她才知道，是因为我老婆区别对待让她感到很委屈。</p>\n<p>我老婆给我女儿吃哈根达斯，却给她吃普通雪糕。</p>\n<p>我老婆给我女儿吃牛排，却给她吃烤肠。</p>\n<p>这个小女孩 5 岁了，她父母离婚多年，一直是老人在带，内心非常敏感。</p>\n<p>她感觉我老婆不喜欢自己，感觉很委屈，就躲在躲被里哭。</p>\n<p>应该如何处理？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1722571670, "replies": 57, "id": 1061982}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_large.png?m=1542423096", "name": "guangzhou", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_normal.png?m=1542423096", "title": "广州", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou", "topics": 1345, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Guangzhou", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096", "stars": 1427, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 20, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 466694, "username": "Jax922", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Jax922", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f12d320bb04541c1cc25e79f570b61c6?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f12d320bb04541c1cc25e79f570b61c6?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f12d320bb04541c1cc25e79f570b61c6?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1579934879, "last_modified": 1579934879}, "last_reply_by": "hanssx", "last_touched": 1722574660, "title": "本人硕士毕业，求 V 友推荐广州高校教师岗？",